{"tid":1252495,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新西蘭移民局地圖標示移除以色列，改為標註巴勒斯坦捱批","createTime":"2019-06-23T04:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:17:40.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc849e7dfbba0493948cb73cc6408dca959e723f","tid":1252495,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T04:57:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2827493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2827493&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaNXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=3c81b742\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2827493&h=9afb4e4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2827493</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕紐西蘭移民局官網日前發布一份介紹中東地區移民現況的文件，不料在17日時被爆出，地圖中完全不存在以色列，只標註了巴勒斯坦和東耶路撒冷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，地圖上不只抹滅以色列的存在，還將東耶路撒冷列為巴勒斯坦首都，然而該地區長年來存在主權爭議，情況敏感複雜，也因此引發外界質疑內容不當。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以色列紐西蘭研究所長邱奇（Ashley Church）指責：「這樣的冒犯讓人難以置信，就如同將英國地圖的蘇格蘭和威爾斯抹消，並將整個不列顛群島稱為英格蘭沒兩樣。」他指出，文件中沒有提到巴勒斯坦的恐怖主義，卻有提到以色列在2000年的「第二次巴勒斯坦大起義」（Second Intifada）中大規模鎮壓巴勒斯坦人。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭教會強調，移民局長必須立刻為此道歉，並進行相關調查，找出誰應該為此事負責，採取相關措施確保類似情況不再發生。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，經過大量網友投訴，目前紐西蘭移民局已將文件下架，不過仍有不少截圖在網上流傳。"},{"pid":"82aad7ac7962937ccc8f916b7ee2e81fca797cda","tid":1252495,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d322713e77e0c3940a309c47d68dd933e1a601c1","tid":1252495,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b4d22e391ba5a5ce94ca2b518b1986704442a7","tid":1252495,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274d82982dc012e82d2712965d8c445758063759","tid":1252495,"uid":199334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T05:59:42.000Z","msg":"約旦河西岸反而變左約旦嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94609a9261bf0f634e9934416b01298a893ebddc","tid":1252495,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T08:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}